nd gulps down more than ten ounces of blood."},{"version":"ruby","text":"GOLBAT loves to drink the blood of living things. It is particularly active in the pitch black of night. This POK\u00e9MON flits around in the night skies, seeking fresh blood."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"GOLBAT bites down on prey with its four fangs and drinks the victim\u2019s blood. It becomes active on inky dark moonless nights, flying around to attack people and POK\u00e9MON."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Its fangs easily puncture even thick animal hide. It loves to feast on the blood of people and POK\u00e9MON. It flits about in darkness and strikes from behind."},{"version":"firered","text":"It clamps down on its prey with needle- sharp fangs and drains over 10 ounces of blood in one gulp."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Once it bites, it will not stop draining energy from the victim even if it gets too heavy to fly."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It loves the blood of humans and Pok\u00e9mon. It flies around at night in search of neck veins."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Once it starts sucking blood, it does not stop until it is full. It flies at night in search of prey."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Its sharp fangs puncture the toughest of hides and have small holes for greedily sucking blood."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"However hard its victim\u2019s hide may be, it punctures with sharp fangs and gorges itself with blood."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It can drink more than 10 ounces of blood at once. If it has too much, it gets heavy and flies clumsily."},{"version":"black","text":"Its sharp fangs puncture the toughest of hides and have small holes for greedily sucking blood."},{"version":"white","text":"Its sharp fangs puncture the toughest of hides and have small holes for greedily sucking blood."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Flitting around in the dead of night, it sinks its fangs into its prey and drains a nearly fatal amount of blood."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Flitting around in the dead of night, it sinks its fangs into its prey and drains a nearly fatal amount of blood."},{"version":"x","text":"Once it bites, it will not stop draining energy from the victim even if it gets too heavy to fly."},{"version":"y","text":"Once it starts sucking blood, it does not stop until it is full. It flies at night in search of prey."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Golbat loves to drink the blood of living things. It is particularly active in the pitch black of night. This Pok\u00e9mon flits around in the night skies, seeking fresh blood."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Golbat bites down on prey with its four fangs and drinks the victim\u2019s blood. It becomes active on inky dark moonless nights, flying around to attack people and Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"sun","text":"Its thick fangs are hollow like straws, making them unexpectedly fragile. These fangs are specialized for sucking blood."},{"version":"moon","text":"Sometimes they drink so much blood, they can\u2019t fly anymore. Then they fall to the ground and become food for other Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Every once in a while, you\u2019ll see a Golbat that\u2019s missing some fangs. This happens when hunger drives it to try biting a Steel-type Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"They can suck down over 10 ounces of blood in one go. They have been known to drink so much blood that they can no longer fly."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"It attacks in a stealthy manner, without warning. Its sharp fangs are used to bite and to suck blood."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"It attacks in a stealthy manner, without warning. Its sharp fangs are used to bite and to suck blood."},{"version":"sword","text":"It loves to drink other creatures\u2019 blood. It\u2019s said that if it finds others of its kind going hungry, it sometimes shares the blood it\u2019s gathered."},{"version":"shield","text":"Its feet are tiny, but this Pok\u00e9mon walks skillfully. It sneaks up on sleeping prey before sinking in its fangs and slurping up blood."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"It sinks its sharp fangs into other creatures and slurps up their blood. A closer look at the fangs reveals that they are hollow and akin to straws."}],"evo":{"name":"zubat","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"golbat","level":1,"min_level":22,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"crobat","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":160,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/42.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/42.png","capture":90,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":15,"ev":{"speed":2},"forms":[]}